{"tid":2329212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"左報借梁振英言論施壓林鄭促推全民檢測 《文匯》社論叫港府查找防疫不足","createTime":"2020-12-17T05:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T05:28:31.000Z","uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"919ee7ac1be1c860f35d4b81c4f74d9432574ff7","tid":2329212,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"blue\">全世界講緊疫苗，建制仲講緊全民檢測，睇來中共好多試劑去唔到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私煙例子告訴我們，測試完過幾日都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n第4波疫情大爆發之際，建制陣營亦爆發「內戰」。全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英昨發長文就強推全民檢測「文攻」林鄭政府後，向來與林鄭針鋒相對的全國政協常委何柱國旗下的《星島日報》，及由中聯辦操控的《文匯報》及《大公報》今日亦「附和」，透過引述和詳細報道梁振英相關言論向林鄭施壓。其中《星島》批評林鄭月娥政府拒從內地推行強制全民檢測或是因為「避難」，「說到底是沒有足夠的闖難關意志」。《文匯》則指港府應「查找本港防疫的不足，堵塞漏洞、彌補短板」，促港府「拿出更大的擔當和魄力」和「積極作為」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/LISX452ULVCUHCD2FBP7TMPNKQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QBuwWHN7x4eqL8akawP35J9Vf-ywP5nrSdQBmDrNsKZPLvAXsGmeiKMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FLISX452ULVCUHCD2FBP7TMPNKQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QBuwWHN7x4eqL8akawP35J9Vf-ywP5nrSdQBmDrNsKZPLvAXsGmeiKMU&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28dOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=06c58cbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FLISX452ULVCUHCD2FBP7TMPNKQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0QBuwWHN7x4eqL8akawP35J9Vf-ywP5nrSdQBmDrNsKZPLvAXsGmeiKMU&h=6ba5009f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/LISX452ULVCUHCD2FBP7TMPNKQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0QBuwWHN7x4eqL8akawP35J9Vf-ywP5nrSdQBmDrNsKZPLvAXsGmeiKMU</a>"}]}